color='#FF9900'>意志之力</font>：额外真实伤害<br><font color='#FF9900'>虚弱溃散</font>：提升技能宽度并缓速所有目标<br><font color='#FF9900'>超能解放</font>：处决低生命的目标","image":{"full":"SyndraPassive.png","sprite":"passive4.png","group":"passive","x":48,"y":48,"w":48,"h":48}},"recommended":[]}}}